License:          GPLv3
BuildRequires:    fpc >= 2.4.0, lazarus >= 0.9.28, PackageKit-glib-devel >= 0.5.6, glib2-devel, gtk2-devel, fpc-src, libqt4intf5, sqlite-devel, PolicyKit-devel
